					| My Recommended Businesses
				// Recommended Busines List
				section#recommendedBusinessList.admin-blocks
					p Here you will see all the businesses that you have worked with and have had a pleasant experience with and can recommend those businesses to others. When users visit your profile page, they will be able to see the businesses you have recommended and can decide whether they want to work with them. When a user sees a company in another user&rsquo;s recommended list, it shows the business is pleasant to work with and provide quality service.
